title: THURSDAY - Week 17 playoff scenarios 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Week 17 playoff scenarios 2020
description:
Washington can clinch a playoff birth with a win over the Eagles, but will they have Alex Smith (0:14) under center? The Cowboys have won 3 straight to keep them in the playoff picture and head coach Mike McCarthy says they're playing their best football of the season (0:46). The Ravens are in a "win and in" scenario (1:11) as Lamar Jackson will be out to make some NFL history (1:53). Ben Roethlisberger (2:16) and Patrick Mahomes (3:09) both sitting out the regular season finale. Plus, the Bills Mafia gets some good news (3:19)
